I admit.

294
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:57,119
When I signed Wen Xiao Nuan,

295
00:17:58,410 --> 00:18:00,650
it was because she looks like Han Hui back then.

296
00:18:01,650 --> 00:18:03,839
But now, whatever happens between Wen Xiao Nuan and Mr. Ye...

297
