Where's my handsome brother-in-law?

333
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:45,199
Xiao Kai, stop talking nonsense.

334
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,200
He's in the doctor's office.

335
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,759
