340
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:02,960
Xiao Jing.

341
00:20:04,039 --> 00:20:06,200
When can I be discharged?

342
00:20:07,480 --> 00:20:08,559
I'm afraid...

343
00:20:08,839 --> 00:20:10,759
I'll delay the filming.

344
00:20:11,170 --> 00:20:12,598
Xiao Jing, you're injured.

345
00:20:12,599 --> 00:20:14,169
Why are you worried about other things?

346
00:20:14,170 --> 00:20:15,920
Your health is the most important.

347
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,319
It's okay.

348
00:20:17,599 --> 00:20:18,650
I can do it.

349
00:20:18,759 --> 00:20:19,759
You can't.

350
00:20:21,559 --> 00:20:22,799
My handsome brother-in-law.

351
00:20:24,720 --> 00:20:26,649
Fei Mo, do you still remember me?

352
00:20:26,650 --> 00:20:28,118
I'm her younger brother, Wen Kai.

353
00:20:28,119 --> 00:20:29,240
Do you remember me?

354
00:20:29,279 --> 00:20:31,240
Xiao Kai, stop it.

355
00:20:32,839 --> 00:20:33,960
Fei Mo.

356
00:20:34,119 --> 00:20:35,119
Go.

357
00:20:36,799 --> 00:20:37,839
Fei Mo.

358
00:20:44,519 --> 00:20:45,599
Fei Mo.

359
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:47,410
All the best.

360
00:20:48,319 --> 00:20:49,410
Xiao Kai.

361
00:21:00,170 --> 00:21:01,919
I'll get his autograph for you when he comes back.

362
00:21:01,920 --> 00:21:02,920
Sure.

363
00:21:05,559 --> 00:21:06,599
Handsome, right?

364
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,200
- Aunt. - Handsome guy.

365
00:21:14,410 --> 00:21:15,440
You're back.

366
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,559
- You look good. - Aunt.

367
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:21,479
Just half a year and you've gotten prettier.

368
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:22,679
- Have I? - You look younger.

369
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:23,719
Really?

370
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,920
If we go out for a walk,

371
00:21:25,079 --> 00:21:27,119
everyone will think we're dating.

372
00:21:27,759 --> 00:21:28,919
All right.

373
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:29,959
You're such a sweet talker.

374
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:31,079
- Let's go. - Let's go.

375
00:21:31,359 --> 00:21:32,359
Let's go inside.

376
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:36,839
So I rejected the other jobs...

377
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,240
and came back.

378
00:21:38,839 --> 00:21:41,039
That's how he coaxed you to come back to ac?

379
00:21:41,319 --> 00:21:42,559
Tell me about it.

380
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:45,119
For his little girlfriend, Wen Xiao Nuan,

381
00:21:45,519 --> 00:21:47,200
I came back from abroad to act.

382
00:21:47,559 --> 00:21:48,650
And this is how he treats me.

383
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,170
He won't let me go out...

384
00:21:50,559 --> 00:21:51,959
or get photographed by the reporters.

385
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,839
I really don't know how she puts up with him.

386
00:21:54,759 --> 00:21:56,039
Wen Xiao Nuan?

387
00:21:57,839 --> 00:22:00,440
I wonder when Fei Mo will pursue her successfully.

388
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,319
They're not official?

389
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,200
You know his temper.

390
00:22:06,759 --> 00:22:08,559
Making him say nice things...

391
00:22:08,839 --> 00:22:10,559
is harder than climbing to the sky.

392
00:22:11,559 --> 00:22:12,599
However,

393
00:22:13,359 --> 00:22:15,559
I quite like Wen Xiao Nuan.

394
00:22:15,839 --> 00:22:18,359
If things work out between them,

395
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:20,480
I'd be happy to see it happen.

396
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,358
You're praising her.

397
00:22:23,359 --> 00:22:24,359
She must be nice.

398
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,640
A hero rescuing a damsel in distress.

399
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:27,960
What a great opportunity.

400
00:22:28,079 --> 00:22:29,319
He didn't make it in time.

401
00:22:30,039 --> 00:22:32,319
Fei Mo? Forget it.

402
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:35,079
It's good enough that he didn't make her angry.

403
00:22:37,279 --> 00:22:38,599
That reminds me.

404
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,880
Listen.

405
00:22:41,160 --> 00:22:42,279
You have to help him.

406
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:51,119
No problem. Leave it to me.

407
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:52,879
- Okay. - Aunt, have some tea.

408
00:22:52,880 --> 00:22:53,959
It's a deal then.

409
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,440
- It's a deal. - Okay.

410
00:22:56,559 --> 00:22:58,519
You're not going anywhere until the splint is removed.

411
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:03,519
Mr. Ye, are you here to see me?

412
00:23:08,039 --> 00:23:09,720
I'm here to see an uncle.

413
00:23:10,319 --> 00:23:11,960
I'm only seeing you in passing.

414
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:21,839
I want some of Jia Yi's soup.

415
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:52,518
It's hot. So hot.

416
00:23:52,519 --> 00:23:53,720
Blow on it.

417
00:24:09,759 --> 00:24:11,880
I'm talking about the soup.

418
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:13,799
It's hot.

419
00:24:18,960 --> 00:24:20,079
Then...

420
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,359
are you still going to drink it?

421
00:24:31,319 --> 00:24:34,480
I want to go back to the set soon.

422
00:24:34,839 --> 00:24:35,839
No.

423
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:38,319
The doctor said you can't go anywhere.

424
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,720
You have to stay here and recuperate.

425
00:24:40,119 --> 00:24:41,880
How do you know what the doctor said?

426
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,799
Aren't you only seeing me in passing?

427
00:24:46,880 --> 00:24:48,400
In short, you're not going anywhere.

428
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,279
You can only stay here and recuperate.

429
00:24:50,640 --> 00:24:51,720
Don't think too much.

430
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,400
What are you so happy about?

431
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:38,960
Nothing.

432
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,480
Nothing?

433
00:25:44,279 --> 00:25:45,359
Come on, slowly.

434
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,000
Jia Yi.

435
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:52,200
Say.

436
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:54,559
Does he like me...

437
00:25:54,759 --> 00:25:57,079
a little bit?

438
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:01,799
You like him.

439
00:26:02,960 --> 00:26:04,439
I don't like him.

440
00:26:04,440 --> 00:26:06,200
Why would I like him?

441
00:26:06,759 --> 00:26:10,160
He's sharp-tongued and picky.

442
00:26:10,359 --> 00:26:12,519
He's a monster and a pervert.

443
00:26:12,680 --> 00:26:14,480
No, he's not that kind of person.

444
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,640
He's not?

445
00:26:18,119 --> 00:26:19,640
Jia Yi, you've gone bad.

446
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:21,720
Okay. Easy now.

447
00:26:21,839 --> 00:26:22,920
Don't hurt yourself.

448
00:26:24,039 --> 00:26:25,119
Silly girl.

449
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,879
Nuan Nuan, take care.

450
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,880
I'm leaving.

451
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,440
Xiao Nuan.

452
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:43,799
Why are you here?

453
00:27:43,839 --> 00:27:45,000
Jia Yi just left.

454
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:48,920
I'm just here to visit you.

455
00:27:51,720 --> 00:27:53,039
Just to visit me?

456
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:55,200
Yes.

457
00:27:58,480 --> 00:28:01,359
But since Jia Yi just left,

458
00:28:02,680 --> 00:28:04,519
I can only talk to these fruits.

459
00:28:05,440 --> 00:28:07,599
No, Xiao Nuan.

460
00:28:08,519 --> 00:28:09,640
I'm sorry.

461
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:12,799
Xiao Nuan.

462
00:28:14,319 --> 00:28:16,079
I really don't know what to do.

463
00:28:18,759 --> 00:28:20,039
I went to see Jia Yi.

464
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:21,720
She's been cold to me.

465
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:25,278
I didn't want to upset her,

466
00:28:25,279 --> 00:28:27,359
so I stopped bothering her.

467
00:28:28,079 --> 00:28:30,119
She's really mad this time.

468
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:33,160
But I swear. I'm serious about her.

469
00:28:35,480 --> 00:28:36,519
Can you help me?

470
00:28:41,400 --> 00:28:43,359
Jia Yi is a kind girl.

471
00:28:44,559 --> 00:28:46,200
She trusts people easily.

472
00:28:47,279 --> 00:28:48,559
She's also very smart.

473
00:28:49,640 --> 00:28:51,759
She knew everything about you, but she didn't expose you...

474
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,839
and waited for you to confess.

475
00:28:56,599 --> 00:28:58,880
I helped you hide it from her...

476
00:29:00,000 --> 00:29:01,200
because I thought...

477
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,799
