478
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:07,559
I also hoped that someone...

479
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:09,839
could take her out of the past...

480
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,480
and start over.

481
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:16,079
We all saw...

482
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:17,960
what you've done for her.

483
00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:20,720
I believe that you truly love her.

484
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:24,279
Actually, that day,

485
00:29:24,440 --> 00:29:26,319
