504
00:30:25,839 --> 00:30:26,960
Now we're talking.

505
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:28,880
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

506
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,359
But I'm telling you.

507
00:30:30,599 --> 00:30:31,680
If you...

508
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:33,680
Be careful.

509
00:30:33,681 --> 00:30:35,278
If you make her sad again,

510
00:30:35,279 --> 00:30:36,319
