511
00:30:37,119 --> 00:30:38,200
Don't worry.

512
00:30:38,599 --> 00:30:40,160
I'll make her happy.

513
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:42,039
I believe you.

514
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:45,640
Come in.

515
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,039
Mr. Jiang.

516
00:30:50,319 --> 00:30:51,480
