518
00:30:55,759 --> 00:30:57,119
That's just an excuse.

519
00:30:57,759 --> 00:30:58,799
What did Han Hui say?

520
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,558
Are there any other projects recently?

521
00:31:05,559 --> 00:31:07,119
